results.response:
~L1: Per user, allow at most 100 requests per 60-second window. If a response is 429, retry with exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s, 8s, ...) until success or retry limit.

~L2:
#cfg {rl:{key:"user_id" max_req:100 win_s:60} rty:{on:429 mode:"exp" delays_ms:[1000,2000,4000,8000,16000,32000]}}
?snd @net {usr:$user_id req:$req} ->$res
^if {$res.code==429} <<
  ^ea {$cfg.rty.delays_ms} ->$d <<
    !run @proc {op:"sleep" ms:$d}
    ?snd @net {usr:$user_id req:$req} ->$res
    ^if {$res.code!=429} {^br}
  >>
>>
^rt {$res}

